Euro Region Needs Own Finance Minister, Steinmeier Tells Bild

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-06-27T06:44:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/euro-region-needs-own-finance-minister-steinmeier-tells-bild.html
The euro area needs its own finance
minister to give the single currency’s fiscal policy “a face,”
German opposition leader Frank-Walter Steinmeier told  Bild
newspaper  in an interview.  Steinmeier,  Germany ’s former foreign minister and vice
chancellor in Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s first-term government,
said the time for national solutions to economic and monetary
problems in the euro area is over, the German newspaper cited
him as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
